headline: Shelf-Stable Food Stocks Q1 In Review: SunOpta (NASDAQ:STKL) Vs Peers
summary: The end of an earnings season can be a great time to discover new stocks and assess how companies are handling the current business environment. Let’s take a look at how SunOpta (NASDAQ:STKL) and the rest of the shelf-stable food stocks fared in Q1.
